Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.65,0:00:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.52,0:00:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.06,0:00:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.97,0:00:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.74,0:00:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.65,0:00:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.25,0:00:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.66,0:00:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.80,0:01:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.93,0:01:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.27,0:01:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.84,0:01:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.45,0:01:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.92,0:01:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.39,0:01:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.47,0:02:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四…四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.32,0:02:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.71,0:02:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#32 神秘的雞蛋?\N四谷的危險禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,原來不是鬧鐘在響啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我要開門囉,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開吧,開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的吵什麼吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我不是在作夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是四谷給你的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是跟四谷吵架了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.25,0:04:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷跟人吵架\N為了洩憤就會給人雞蛋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.59,0:04:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷會給人東西\N這種事是不可能發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太異常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非比尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有做什麼壞事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是危險物品?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是不會爆炸啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要嚇我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是想想看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果心血來潮\N把那顆雞蛋吃了的話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.37,0:05:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代竟然把我給他的雞蛋吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.31,0:05:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好可憐的雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果沒有吃的話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.68,0:05:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送給五代的雞蛋\N他竟然不吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.89,0:05:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好可憐的雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,沒錯\N他一定會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是收到了一個燙手山芋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.87,0:06:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是生雞蛋?還是水煮蛋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.74,0:06:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,保存的期限不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.71,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是生的還是熟的\N先放到冰箱裡去比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,一定是滾掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.66,0:06:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜一點\N萬一弄破了就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底滾到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雞…雞蛋呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋沒事,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是要送給我的禮物?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.38,0:07:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,怎麼辦?\N五代,你好討厭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個這個\N我想看的就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.39,0:08:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?你討厭看這種電影嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個雞蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟是要送給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是只是要我幫他保管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我還是搞不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,把那個翻過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保溫不就好了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.34,0:08:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷想孵雞蛋\N所以一直將它保溫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,因為孵不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.72,0:08:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才找你代打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這顆蛋會孵出什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.26,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果照妳說的\N可能是一隻小雞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是一隻小蜥蜴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.97,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.77,0:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這顆蛋是四谷的蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.51,0:09:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從蛋裡面會跑出一個\N小小的四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就只是一顆蛋嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是還給他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.88,0:09:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.68,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候他叫我還給他\N我怎麼受得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷還沒回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,兩份牛丼是嗎\N好,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.80,0:10:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸口沾染牛肉的薄情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣\N就不能放在冰箱裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而要保溫才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我想應該不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先,先來確認一下\N這是生蛋還是熟蛋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是熟蛋就沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.09,0:10:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是生的\N還是保溫起來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打破看得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這本烹飪書裡面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷的雞蛋,借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個,只是普通的雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.68,0:11:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我媽對這顆蛋很有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不是雞蛋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.88,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你媽是對我有興趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,賢太郎,不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書裡沒寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我記得在哪裡看過\N分辨的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.22,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一顆生蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生蛋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果是顆生蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,是一顆生蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.26,0:12:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,等四谷回來了\N我會把事情跟他說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.63,0:12:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,有些人說得通\N有些人怎麼說都說不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.31,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶,中計了,中計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看,真正的蛋在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢…賢太郎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.40,0:13:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說過多少次了\N不可以糟蹋食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,妳很煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你去洗澡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才驚擾妳了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把這顆蛋帶去澡堂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.79,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,與其放在房裡\N這樣我比較安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家雖然沒有惡意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著這種會破的東西\N真的很麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要顧到四谷回來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.94,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.34,0:14:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,他說不定躲在某處看著你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,這個笑話不好笑嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.99,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜到連水聲都聽得一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單寂寞到變成一條魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚四谷又出現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋生蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天說不定會變得更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是賢太郎幹的好事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓圈裡有個''一''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,我也做了記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.14,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼記號?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我畫了一個圈\N裡面有個平假名''yo''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.92,0:15:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太\N妳平常都會在蛋上面做記號嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是''圓圈一''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是,這個也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.27,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,全部都是''圓圈一''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,這不是四谷的雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不同嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家的蛋,妳要賠我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來,拿走蛋的人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,把蛋還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.08,0:16:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不還的話\N我就要拉扯你的關節喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以後不教你寫作業了喔\N可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給你,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,賢太郎,不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一顆才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.44,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分辨生蛋和熟蛋的方法…嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.82,0:16:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,因為你很會做菜\N所以我想你可能會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不巧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳問這個做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.59,0:17:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情是福是禍不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能隨便弄破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這顆蛋這麼危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.03,0:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁這顆蛋還沒破之前\N趕快把它扔掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持有人是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N那就更應該馬上把它打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他跟你要的話\N拿另外一顆還他不就得了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.42,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼聰明\N拿另外一顆還給他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會看出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的看得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有勇氣賭賭看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.51,0:17:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,給我站住,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.27,0:18:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就成功了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?我不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.62,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,現在只能拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼求你都不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是\N笑嘻嘻兒童電話詢問室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.40,0:19:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要分辨生蛋和熟蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼鬼地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷在這裡生活嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,原來是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有什麼感覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得味道有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你有腸胃藥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼奇怪的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.04,0:20:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情不要知道比較幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,到底是什麼?告訴我\N我們是好朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.46,0:20:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是已經煮熟的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.12,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個水煮蛋沒錯\N有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.60,0:21:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面音響4點35分20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.80,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面音響4點35分30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行得通嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷一定看得出來\N這不是原來的蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是\N他對食物非常內行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不行也要試試看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,得先把水煮蛋做好再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.33,0:21:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.50,0:21:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖睡你的覺吧,少廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.00,0:21:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,火再開大一點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.00,0:21:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能用這顆蛋騙過四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.87,0:22:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.54,0:22:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火開得太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.38,0:22:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.72,0:23:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家的蛋一定要還給我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.29,0:23:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃下去的雞蛋\N有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.36,0:23:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代你說說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.44,0:23:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…肚子好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.98,0:23:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,誰叫你要偷吃四谷的蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.26,0:23:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,救救我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.86,0:23:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明月啊,朋友聲聲叫痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.06,0:23:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撿來的蛋不該隨便亂吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.77,0:23:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她寄來了一張這樣的明信片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.51,0:23:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫人實在無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夾在惣一郎日記裡的明信片\N究竟是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.78,0:24:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.51,0:24:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「日記的衝擊!\N惣一郎有女朋友?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.18,0:24:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有寄過這種憂愁的明信片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.91,0:24:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.85,0:24:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.82,0:24:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.86,0:24:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.97,0:25:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷彿\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.71,0:25:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
